{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "U7CO2DUNYT7QXYYGMH75H3F5666I3J6U",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "501005116",
    "title": "第四幕　You're beautiful",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "今……みんなの期待が\nどうしようもなく怖いんだ。",
            "enText": "Now…… I'm helplessly afraid of what \neveryone's expectations are.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 8647828658400880360
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -1807990634720761604
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2486339869522447137,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの日からずっと、恐怖を乗り越える方法を\n模索する日々が続いていた。",
            "enText": "Ever since that day, I've been searching for \nways to overcome my fear.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（何かいい方法は……）",
                    "enText": "(What's the best way to do it: ……)",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -4070848799528307841
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": 4597392970722835643
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 743550571100286551,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "頭を悩ませながらトレーナー室へ向かうと――",
            "enText": "I headed for the trainer's \noffice, racking my brains.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "pathId": -1108429996347567434,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "フジキセキが、\n舞台のDVDを食い入るように見ていた。",
            "enText": "Fujikiseki was devouring a DVD of the play.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 197,
                    "pathId": -686225214821242958
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 6403381715267392519
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -320398163274001525,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "あっ。トレーナーさん、おかえりなさい！\nお邪魔しています。",
            "enText": "Ah. Welcome back, trainer! \nI'm sorry to bother you.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "これは？",
                    "enText": "What's this?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -4352894072989653103
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 6843468325096672333
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -7529654232784227427
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9174689694710469952,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "母の舞台のDVDだよ。",
            "enText": "It's a DVD of my mother's play.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 2737435813307758307
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": 7351840229540053612
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 4782685242730996649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5215815943509986400,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "……実はね、母が舞台の上で恐れている\nところを、私は見たことがないんだ。",
            "enText": "I've never seen my mother afraid on stage. ……",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 2183086429145470129
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": 1714922504920708079
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -1697460084014155766
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6858541410818763350,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "たとえ眼前に何千もの観客がいたとしても、\r\n関係ない。誰よりも自由に舞台を駆けるのさ。",
            "enText": "It doesn't matter if there are thousands of \nspectators in front of me. I run on stage \nmore freely than anyone else.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 4778009670576920789
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -5829982331163078867
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8055480823019102502,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "あれほどの期待を前に、\nなぜ恐怖せずにいられるのか気になって。",
            "enText": "I was curious as to how you could be so \nfearless in the face of so much anticipation.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 6628134948643605340
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 8511651283299302162
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7727603782837405494,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "それが天才ゆえのなせる業なのか、\nもしくはどこかで乗り越えたのか……。",
            "enText": "I wonder if that's the work of genius, or if \nshe got over it somewhere. ……",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 8116476919344625969
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -1454399723801947922
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3704758816739448527,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "どちらかはわからないけれど、きっとここに、\n次へ進むためのヒントがあると思うんだ。",
            "enText": "I don't know which one it is, \nbut I'm sure there is a clue here \nthat will help me move on.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -9068321972115883851
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 6780974441148891841
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7108913293380888065,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どうやら、フジキセキも同じことを\n感じていたようだ。それならば――",
            "enText": "Apparently, Fujikiseki felt \nthe same way. In that case―",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺も一緒に見ていいかな",
                    "enText": "Can I watch with you?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私も一緒に見ていいかな",
                    "enText": "May I watch with you?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 8597452422107151550
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 7848673718377131426
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3816432474600816593,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "もちろん！\r\nそのつもりで、持ってきたからね。",
            "enText": "Of course! That's what I meant, I brought it.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -7214104394007006662
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": 3840139726017839943
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5653135781276468521,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "舞台は近世のフランス。\r\n王妃が牢獄に捕らえられるところから\n物語は始まる。",
            "enText": "The story takes place in early modern \nFrance. The story begins with the \nqueen's capture in prison.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -4167722216997780541
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": 8678631933490951360
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8948518389961484906,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキの母親",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『ひとつ願いが叶うのならば。ああ、\nあの美しきオーストリアへ帰りたい……！』",
            "enText": "If I could make one wish come true. \nOh, I wish I could go back to that \nbeautiful Austria: ……!\"",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "pathId": 5842932155579155467,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女の悲痛な叫びとともに\n軽快な音楽が鳴り響き、照度が一気に上がる。",
            "enText": "Light music rings out with her plaintive \ncries, and the illumination level \nrises dramatically.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "pathId": 1284656250665359790,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "煤にまみれた王妃は、いつしか可憐な\r\n少女となり自然あふれる城内を駆けていた。",
            "enText": "The queen, covered in soot, became a pretty \ngirl and ran around the castle, which was \nfull of nature.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "pathId": -8496622943792042363,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "……この舞台は母の1人芝居なんだ。\r\nたった1人で、悲劇の王妃の生涯と\nその周囲の人々を演じていく。",
            "enText": "…… This play is my mother's one-woman \nshow. With only one person, she plays \nthe life of the tragic queen and and \nthe people around her.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 216,
                    "pathId": 5796528601121413302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 161,
                    "pathId": -1700497338528611853
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5550736215943853538,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "給仕係の冷たい眼差し、下町の娘の後姿。\n大道芸人の快活な口上と、王の静かな独白。",
            "enText": "The cold gaze of the waiter, the back \nview of the downtown girl. The lively \nspeech of a street performer and the \nquiet monologue of the king.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 6132599848280334737
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -8648331349462018828
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6626432536743723569,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女の役は目まぐるしいほどにコロコロと\n代わり、それでいて混乱することはなく――",
            "enText": "Her roles are dizzyingly varied, \nyet never confusing.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 363776307435288803
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -8412714617727648365
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1351733740289717297,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一言一句で観客を引き込み、\nそれに呼応するように客席から\nため息や小さな悲鳴が漏れ聞こえてくる。",
            "enText": "The audience is drawn in with every word, \nand in response, sighs and small screams \ncan be heard leaking from the seats. sighs \nand small screams are heard leaking from \nthe audience in response.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -6590362882924349177
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -6983301020239946607
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6367556528211403902,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そうして、気づけば彼女が舞台俳優である\r\nということさえ忘れ――",
            "enText": "And then you forget that \nshe's even a stage actor.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "pathId": 1957076112195091673,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "物語はクライマックスを迎えていた。",
            "enText": "The story was reaching its climax.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "pathId": 5215767790803256470,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキの母親",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『私の姿を、貴方だけは焼き付けて。\nその、漆黒の瞳に……！』",
            "enText": "I want you to burn my image in your eyes. In \nyour jet-black eyes, ……!\"",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "pathId": -7618108398649040447,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "1羽の青い鳥が青空へと飛び立ち、\r\n民衆の歓声が轟いて――",
            "enText": "A blue bird flew into the blue sky, and the \npeople roared with joy.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "pathId": 6449682453036538141,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "1人芝居は、長い長い\nスタンディングオベーションで幕を閉じた。",
            "enText": "The one-man show ended with a long, long \nstanding ovation.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "pathId": -6743745273297481585,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "――……圧巻だ。",
            "enText": "―…… It's overwhelming.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": -6104481992950364950
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -4432100698291296926
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4320206056673803107,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ヒントを探すつもりが、気づけば\n純粋に物語を楽しんでしまっていた。",
            "enText": "I intended to look for clues, but I found \nmyself genuinely enjoying the story.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "すごい方なんだな",
                    "enText": "You must be a great guy.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "すごい方なんだね",
                    "enText": "You must be a great guy.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -4951254427217586002
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 4948343005563772981
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3191782598035569762,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "うん。母ほどの舞台俳優は見たことがない。\n身内びいきのようだけど、本当なんだ。",
            "enText": "Yup. I've never seen a stage actor as good as \nmy mother. I know it sounds like I'm being a \nfamily man, but it's true.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 6654332825190932742
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 8973892785496545104
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4577364547377044264,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "ああなりたいと思う人は多いが、\nなれた人はほとんどいない。私を含めてね。",
            "enText": "Many people want to be like them, but few \nhave become them. Including me.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 7760929800215812294
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -5351911262064678177
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -654946688872373793,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "フジキセキの目指す最高のエンターテイナー。\nその姿が少しだけわかったような気がした。",
            "enText": "Fujikiseki aims to be the best entertainer. I \nfelt as if I could understand a little bit of \nwhat she is like.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 7807884960911485207
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 4770478961732357342
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7129924753876049535,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "――でも、やっぱり舞台上の彼女は\n登場人物だね。",
            "enText": "―But she is still a character on stage.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": 2172930372311577836
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -7400490085343639056
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -302564034067840816,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "なにを思っているのかなんて\nわかるわけがなかった。",
            "enText": "There was no way I could know \nwhat she was thinking.",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 6038824632580240982
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -2769347341768280258
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4397400443242888714,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "仲が悪そうにも感じられないし、いっそ\n本人に直接聞くのが早いのではないだろうか。",
            "enText": "I don't get the sense that they don't seem to \nget along, and I think it would be quicker to \nask her directly.",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いっそ直接聞きに行ってみる？",
                    "enText": "Why don't we just go and ask them directly?",
                    "nextBlock": 35
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 7960020372818334290
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -8604970767724917647
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6834583772519629641,
            "blockIdx": 34
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "ん、うん……。",
            "enText": "Hmm, yeah. ……",
            "nextBlock": 36,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -7223443814322465936
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -1562949336528729530
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -606018019864140851,
            "blockIdx": 35
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "……実を言うとね、少し敬遠してたんだ。\n理解してもらえなかったらと思うと怖くて。",
            "enText": "……To tell you the truth, I was a \nbit hesitant to do so. I was afraid \nthat they wouldn't understand.",
            "nextBlock": 37,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 7040566043218808888
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -1805322429768161500
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7690865871959319601,
            "blockIdx": 36
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
